GNU MongoDb GUI Tool
====================

Pre-condition
-------------

You need get installed and configurated:

 + JDK 1.6
 + Apache Maven 2.2

Installation (install + run)
------------

 > sh bin/setup.sh
 > sh bin/run.sh

or

 > mvn clean install
 > java -jar target/monguito-0.1.one-jar.jar

Beta version 0.1.1
------------------

- Show data bases
- Show collection
- Find: 
    > db.<collection>.find().skip(xx).limit(yy) from a simple button.
    > Simple paginate
- Create collection
- Remove collection
- Truncate (remove and create) collection
- Insert field in collection
- Remove selected field from collection
- Create DB
- Destroy DB
- Edit selected field
- Configurate multiples connections.
- Set look and feel
- Show selected elements
- Filter:
    > Element by String


